---
id: org.dxos.plugin.chessCom
name: ChessComPlugin
version: 0.1.0
---

Chess.com account integration for DXOS Composer. Links a Chess.com username,
syncs archived games into a local feed as `Game` objects (chess variant), and
displays them in a masonry gallery rendered by plugin-chess game cards.

## Extensions

| Term        | URI                            |
|-------------|--------------------------------|
| `type`      | `org.dxos.mdl.type@1.0`       |
| `feat`      | `org.dxos.mdl.feat@1.0`       |
| `test`      | `org.dxos.mdl.test@1.0`       |
| `component` | `org.dxos.mdl.component@1.0`  |
| `op`        | `org.dxos.mdl.op@1.0`         |

## Types

```mdl
type ChessComAccount
  fields:
    username: string @label/title
    playerId?: number
    profileUrl?: string
    followers?: number
    country?: string
    lastOnline?: number
    joined?: number
    status?: string
    isStreamer?: boolean
    verified?: boolean
    league?: string
    streamingPlatforms?: string[]
    games: Ref<Feed>   # Game (org.dxos.type.game) entries with Chess.State variants
  foreignKeys:
    service: chess.com
    id: <username>
  typename: org.dxos.type.chessCom.account
  version: 0.1.0
```

## Components

```mdl
component ChessGameArticle
  desc: Masonry gallery of synced chess games; each tile renders a Game card surface.
  props:
    account: ChessComAccount
  actions:
    syncGames()
  layout: |
    ┌─────────────────────────┐
    │ [Sync games] toolbar    │
    ├─────────────────────────┤
    │ masonry of game cards   │
    └─────────────────────────┘
```

## Operations

```mdl
op SyncGames
  desc: Fetch all archived games from chess.com and append new Game objects to the account feed.
  input:
    account: Ref<ChessComAccount>
  output:
    appended: number
  effects: [http, echo:write]

op ClearSyncedGames
  desc: Replace the account games feed with a fresh empty feed, discarding synced games.
  input:
    account: Ref<ChessComAccount>
  output:
    removed: number
  effects: [echo:write]
```

## Features

```mdl
feat F-1: Create account

  req F-1.1: Create form asks only for Chess.com username.
  req F-1.2: Account is stamped with foreign key `{ source: chess.com, id: username }`.
  req F-1.3: A backing ECHO feed is created for synced games.
```

```mdl
feat F-2: Sync games

  req F-2.1: SyncGames loads player profile fields from the chess.com Published API.
  req F-2.2: SyncGames walks monthly archives and imports each game as a `Game` with `Chess.State` (PGN/FEN).
  req F-2.3: Re-sync does not duplicate games already present in the feed (uuid foreign key).
```

```mdl
feat F-3: Game gallery

  req F-3.1: ChessGameArticle lists games from the account feed in a masonry layout.
  req F-3.2: Each tile renders `AppSurface.CardContent` so plugin-chess supplies the game card.
```

## Acceptance

```mdl
test T-1: Create with username only
  given: user enters username "hhhhthrv"
  then:
    - ChessComAccount.username === "hhhhthrv"
    - foreign key chess.com/hhhhthrv is set
```

```mdl
test T-2: Sync deduplicates games
  given: account with two games already synced
  when: SyncGames runs against the same upstream archive
  then: appended === 0
```
